%!
% Cookbook Example Program from First Printing, Revised 7 Jan 1985
% Program: White Text on a Black Background     Number: 12
%-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
%
newpath                                     % Create the black rectangular
  72 561 moveto                             % background. Since the default
  296 561 lineto                            % color in the Graphics State is
  296 440 lineto                            % black, there is no need to
  72 440 lineto                             % explicitly set the color.
closepath fill
	      
/Helvetica-Bold findfont 14 scalefont       % Usually a bold font will have
  setfont                                   % more presence on a black
					    % background than a medium font.
									    
gsave                                       % Save the current Graphics State
					    % so that it will be unaffected by
					    % changes in color.
  1.0 setgray                               % Change the color to white.
  104 520 moveto
  (Rest at pale evening . . .) show         % The show operator uses the
  104 502 moveto                            % current color in the Graphics
  (A tall slim tree . . .) show             % State. Since we are "drawing"
  104 484 moveto                            % white characters on a black
  (Night coming tenderly) show              % area, it gives the impression of
  104 466 moveto                            % black text on a white background
  (Black like me.) show                     % which has been reversed.
								      
grestore
	
104 398 moveto
(Langston Hughes) show
		      
showpage
